### 6. Create Schedule with Unauthorized Topic (Invalid)
POST {{baseUrl}}/schedules:createOrUpdateByDedup
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tenantId": "hospital-1",
  "ownerService": "appointments",
  "scheduleType": "ONCE",
  "startAtUtc": "2025-10-23T09:00:00Z",
  "topicOrCommand": "billing.invoice.send",
  "payloadJson": {
    "test": "data"
  },
  "dedupKey": "test:unauthorized-topic"
}

