### 17. Clinical Service - Prescription Refill Reminder
POST {{baseUrl}}/schedules:createOrUpdateByDedup
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tenantId": "hospital-1",
  "ownerService": "clinical",
  "scheduleType": "ONCE",
  "startAtUtc": "2025-10-25T09:00:00Z",
  "topicOrCommand": "clinical.prescription.refill.reminder",
  "payloadJson": {
    "prescriptionId": "rx-123",
    "patientId": "patient-456",
    "medication": "Aspirin"
  },
  "dedupKey": "clinical:rx-123:refill-reminder"
}

###

### 18. Patient Registry - Annual Checkup Reminder
POST {{baseUrl}}/schedules:createOrUpdateByDedup
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tenantId": "hospital-1",
  "ownerService": "patient-registry",
  "scheduleType": "ONCE",
  "startAtUtc": "2025-12-01T09:00:00Z",
  "topicOrCommand": "patient-registry.patient.checkup.annual",
  "payloadJson": {
    "patientId": "patient-456",
    "lastCheckup": "2024-12-01"
  },
  "dedupKey": "patient-registry:patient-456:annual-checkup-2025"
}

